Carrying the power of Bane, this adamantine morningstar sports foot-long spikes and has a jagged blade on its pommel.
{"type": "entries", "name": "Sentience", "entries": ["The Bloody End is a sentient lawful evil weapon with an Intelligence of 22, a Wisdom of 18, and a Charisma of 24. It has hearing and {@sense darkvision} out to a range of 120 feet.", "The weapon communicates telepathically with its wielder and can speak, read, and understand Common and Infernal."]}
